casebody.data:
Anthony DOVE
v.
Faye E. DANIELS, Superintendent of Pamlico Corrections No. 131P01-14 Supreme Court of North Carolina. July 25, 2017 Anthony Dove, for Dove, Anthony. Sherri Lawrence, Assistant Attorney General, Matthew Delbridge, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 24th of July 2017 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Lenoir County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 25th of July 2017."
